channel.title: Comments on: Tug Baker’s Top Albums of 2010

item.title: By: Pete
item.dc:creator: Pete
item.description: YES, Tug. Tame Impala = #1 with a bullet. Also, somehow the best show I saw in 2010. I set the bar so high going into it & yet they cleared it. They'll be selling out stadiums in 5 years.
